{"type": "article", "id": 29001, "title": "苹果 CEO 任 Nike 独立董事，以及，Balmain 度假系列不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-07-01T10:13:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2866, "name": "退休"}, {"id": 26755, "name": "董事会"}, {"id": 29655, "name": "白裙"}, {"id": 14026, "name": "度假系列"}, {"id": 1879, "name": "夏威夷"}, {"id": 27751, "name": "旅游市场"}, {"id": 14917, "name": "秋季"}, {"id": 27836, "name": "寝具"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 231, "name": "Apple"}, {"id": 2002, "name": "Balmain"}, {"id": 29656, "name": "For Love and Lemons"}, {"id": 3351, "name": "Miu Miu"}, {"id": 26424, "name": "巴黎欧莱雅"}, {"id": 29657, "name": "Frances Valentine"}, {"id": 1066, "name": "Calvin Klein"}, {"id": 2855, "name": "Tommy Hilfiger"}, {"id": 28590, "name": "雪肌精"}, {"id": 29224, "name": "DFS"}, {"id": 2816, "name": "Kate Spade"}, {"id": 2858, "name": "Tim Cook"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703152151reZbYS7QtEHgT8Fk.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/07/01/tim-cook-joins-nike/\"><b>苹果 CEO Tim Cook 担任 Nike “首席独立董事”</b></a>｜Nike 于今日宣布苹果 CEO Tim Cook 担任集团“首席独立董事”，Tim 于 2005 年加入 Nike 董事会。同时 Nike 创始人 Phil Knight 正式退出董事会，现任总裁兼 CEO Mark Parker 接替董事长职位。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Tommy-Hilfiger-leaves-Paris-Champs-Elysees,709292.html\"><b>Tommy Hilfiger 香榭丽舍大街关店</b></a>｜Tommy Hilfiger 将关闭其在巴黎香榭丽舍大街上的门店，2010 年底开设，面积有 835 平米。据悉，9 月 30 日将是店铺运营最后一天。一旁的 Nike 门店可能会以此扩张店铺面积。PVH 集团则表示，撤出香榭丽舍大街完全不存在任何关于“撤出法国市场”的暗示。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/L-Oreal-acquires-niche-perfumer-Atelier-Cologne,709435.html\"><b>欧莱雅收购香水品牌 Atelier Cologne</b></a>｜巴黎欧莱雅宣布已签署协议收购香水品牌 Atelier Cologne，后者是由  Sylvie Ganter 和 Christophe Cervasel 两人在 2009 年创立，专注于古龙水的品牌。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/skin-care/kose-sekkisei-dfs-group-10473079/\"><b>雪肌精进军美国旅游市场</b></a>｜日本护肤品牌雪肌精与 DFS 集团合作，8 月 1 日开始在夏威夷首府 Honolulu 的免税店 T Galleria 售卖，后者隶属于 DFS 集团。此次合作为雪肌精母公司高丝在本土市场外全球扩张计划中的一部分。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/calvin-klein-modern-cotton-bedding-launch-10469032/\"><b>Calvin Klein  推出寝具</b></a>｜Calvin Klein 将推出属于家居品类的棉质床上用品——Home Modern Cotton Bedding 产品线，7 月 7 日起在 Bloomingdale 百货旗舰店独家上市，8 月 1 日世界范围内的其它门店可以买到。寝具设计的灵感来自 Calvin Klein  经典的内衣系列。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<p>夏季特别的白色裙子，可以看看 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/lookbook/for-love-lemons-white-dresses-summer-romance-2016/\">For Love and Lemons 的</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703152135Ep1d07rjTeKafxYC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703152135hBgP4GcbSHz8Lk60.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703152136ZbOP73fE4ikWIvKx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703152136FPJQmdWpifMDuqtL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, Helvetica, Tahoma, 'Arial sans-serif'; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">Kate Spade 本人离开个人同名品牌后，创立的新品牌</span><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/frances-valentine-second-ad-campaign-10474912/\" style=\"font-family: Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, Helvetica, Tahoma, 'Arial sans-serif'; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"> Frances Valentine 发布第二期广告</a><span style=\"font-family: Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, Helvetica, Tahoma, 'Arial sans-serif'; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">，展示秋季系列：</span></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703152137XYrMIR0Lw9qdeJPs.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703152137crGjQ1PtaM9TVBdN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703152138bT5l2weUziXqJCvR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/shows-reviews/gallery/balmain-resort-2017-10477316/#!46/balmain-resort-2017-73/\">Balmain 2017 度假系列</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703152139YBw0r6j3JVkIZAUb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031521390RmzPrg4isvWdMpD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031521401x0gClPjSioeB6Nz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703152140VtvJw7MzndYA0BHp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703152140bKh2Fu7UQtmxeYzB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703152141kaAmQeBzpWtqMXdD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703152141UZGW7uS9hbO1PAq2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=