演过 Gossip Girl 及《妈妈咪呀》的影星 Amanda Seyfried，近日<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/amanda-seyfriend-miu-miu-fall-2016-campaign/\">为 Miu Miu 2016 秋冬系列拍摄海报</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703152147cDyvKSfz6UdLkr5b.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703152148ZMjpbPYJS0fGuN8F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703152148rzN2W5V1pFAZIkgv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703152149nBJ5vh0PE3Z8reFi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031521497yY4nxMgqKJke9LN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703152150srPmRdOgWwXDBZno.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>另一位在《自杀小队》中饰演“小丑女”的澳大利亚女演员 Margot Robbie，为  Calvin Klein  最新推出的<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/calvin-klein-deep-euphoria-perfume-campaign/\">女士香水“Deep Euphoria”拍摄了广告</a>：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703152150K5SXVTfmg7AtpWCv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}